Twittaddict for Android
------------------------
Finally! A way to prove you spend a lot of time on Twitter!

* Do you know what your Twitter friends are going to tweet before they do?
* Do you always know who tweeted what?

Now you have the chance to show off these important life skills with twittaddict!

* Find out who your Twitter BFF is!
* Are you a twittdominator? Compare scores with Game Center!
* Unlock achievements and become twittawesome!